{"tid":1453454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地有民間記者會 不如出埋民間收音機","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:35:15.000Z","uid":112691,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e42565fd296e4a868a4485ffa05918cb372b0b70","tid":1453454,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"既然我地依家要打輿論戰、民意戰<br />\n我地就要著重同中立、藍絲、政治冷感既人有交流<br />\n有冇諗過藍絲點解會變藍絲<br />\n一嚟冇獨立思考<br />\n二嚟接收資訊既渠道同我地唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多藍絲都係年紀大，唔識上網，或者啱啱識用whatsapp<br />\n所以佢地收到朋友既message就覺得係真係岩唔識過濾<br />\n免費電視得cctvb<br />\n連電視都咁講啵，我地仲唔係暴徒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就慢慢形成兩大對立陣營<br />\nOk講重點<br />\n既然係咁，我地除左連儂牆，就要喺屋企做起<br />\n拎你地個藍芽喇叭出嚟 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做民間收音機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n大大聲播Do you hear the people sing<br />\n大大聲播所有道出事實既新聞媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多新移民地方，尤其北區呢啲多蝗地區<br />\n得閒播下台灣非親中媒體，普通話既新聞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記得11點收音機就休息下啦</span></span><br />\nAirdrop唔好淨係地鐵airdrop!周街行周街send!<br />\n遇到任何深藍生物記得要冷靜解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工已經成功說服左幾位熟客開始變淺黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n運用下我地手上有既野<br />\n大家一齊諗下仲有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上係小弟小小意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩改善屌細力啲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好齋睇呀 做呀<br />\n香港靠我地救架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b043978f